<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>测试与反馈</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Arial}
body{background:#fafafa;padding:30px 15px}
.title{text-align:center;font-size:26px;margin-bottom:25px}
.back{background:#616161;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 20px;margin-bottom:20px;cursor:pointer}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px}
.item{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:25px 10px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 8px #00000013;cursor:pointer}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<button class="back" onclick="location.href='index.html'">← 返回主页</button>
<div class="title">⚙️ 测试与反馈</div>
<div class="main">
<div class="grid">
<div class="grid">

  <button onclick="location.href='l/5.html'">意见反馈</button>
<button onclick="location.href='l/l2.html'">刷新</button>
<button onclick="location.href='l/l3.html'">二维码</button>
<button onclick="location.href='l/l4.html'">性能测试</button>
<button onclick="location.href='l/l1.html'">图像测试</button>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
